lead_paragraph: CJ McCollum had 25 points and seven assists, leading the Portland Trail Blazers to a 112-106 victory over the Denver Nuggets on Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: McCollum Scores 25 as Trail Blazers Beat Nuggets 112-106
